____________________ Geeks Application ____________________
    - Create Application
        python manage.py startapp geeks

    - Add application in INSTALLED_APPS
        INSTALLED_APPS = [
		    	'geeks',
		    ]

    - Creating a geeks model

    - Register the model with admin.site.register()

    - Class Based Views
        - Automatically setup everything
        - Specify which model to create ListView
        - Automatically try to find a template in app_name/modelname_list.html
        - geeks/templates/geeks/geeksmodel_list.html

        - Note : application -> templates -> application -> ........._list.html

    - Create our class based view

    - Create a url path to map the view

